---
By: Papa Ramdas
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 324
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Miracles
---
Miracles only work through your own faith. Where there is no faith there
can be no miracle. So he who wants to perform a miracle can only do so by
the power of faith. From this it is evident that the matter rests entirely
with you.
